                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850112-23-defend346 t17850112-23-punish134"></join>
               Transported for seven years
            </rs>.</p>


               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
